*.env
# Local agent/editor configs that may hold API keys — never commit.
opencode.jsonc
.opencode.json
.mcp.json
# ...but the shipped plugin manifest is a checked-in template (user_config placeholders, no secrets).
!plugin/osint-geoint/.mcp.json
*.log
coverage/
.vite/
.turbo/
# Cloudflare Worker local state + the entire built console bundle. deploy.sh
# rebuilds site/ from apps/web on every deploy — it's an artifact, not source.
.wrangler/
site/
# Anywhere in the tree — the cache lives at apps/api/data/tilecache; the old
# root-anchored pattern missed it and 2.7k PNGs got committed.
**/data/tilecache/
# History playback SQLite store (refills from live data; never commit).
**/data/history.db
**/data/history.db-*
# Ontology local spine (the analyst's graph + assertion history; never commit).
**/data/ontology.db
**/data/ontology.db-*
# Foundry BYO-data store (uploaded datasets + build history; runtime, never commit).
**/data/foundry.db
**/data/foundry.db-*
# Workflows store (saved DAGs + run history + per-workflow memory; runtime).
**/data/workflows.db
**/data/workflows.db-*
.playwright-mcp/
# Dev screenshots / scratch images at the repo root — keep the tree tidy.
# (Real product art lives in code as SVG, or under docs/ if ever needed.)
/*.png
/*.jpg
/*.jpeg
/*.gif
/*.webp
apps/ml/fusion/data/
apps/ml/fusion/runs/
